channel.title: Freijascape (...my new server coming out in 2007!...)
channel.description:
This is my server based off of Testscape and Cheezscape both. It's still under development so don't say this belongs in advertisement!
[img]http://r1.fodey.com/18ad3040afac541308dd1401ae84445c9.1.gif[/img]
[IMG]http://img225.imageshack.us/img225/9977/alberteinsteinfreijadx0.jpg[/img]
[b][i][u]Updates:[/u][/i][/b] NOTE------IM NOT LISTING THEM ALL!!!! Update 1-- Changed everything that said testscape to Freijascape Update 2-- Added some new shops Update 3-- Added Rare Smithing [b]Update 4-- Working on![/b]
Come to the forums at: [url=http://freijascape.smfforfree2.com]Freijascape[/url]
Thanks and ill keep you updated![br][size=1]Posted at: December 20, 2006, 03:56:26 PM[/size][hr]anyone want to comment?
